Class InventoryAction

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatg2001.paths.model.actions.Action
no.ntnu.idatg2001.paths.model.actions.InventoryAction
@Entity public class InventoryAction extends Action
The InventoryAction class represents an action that can be performed by the player on an item in the inventory.
